No. 162,

Misc.

Cooper et al. v. Rust Engineering Co. James G. Wheeler for petitioners. J. D. Inman and E. Palmer James for respondent. Solicitor General Perlman and William S. Tyson filed a memorandum for the United States, as amicus curiae, supporting the petition.

C. A. 6th Cir. Certiorari denied.
